# Rub the API as a docker container 
A docker cli client is installed inside this API. This client cli will contact the target docker server to get the information of that server. This is a cleartext TCP communication on port 2375. Which means the docker server should be accessable remotely via the 2375 port.

Folloeing steps can be followed to expose the the docker demone on port 2375 

Edit/create the file `/etc/docker/daemon.json` 
